  "body": "# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/links.png\" alt=\"Our Links\">\n\n<center>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/SafBQVETQn\" style=\"float: left;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/button/discord.png\" alt=\"Discord Link\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/IleafDevelopment\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/button/ko-fi.png\" alt=\"Support us\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ileafcore\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/button/curseforge.png\" alt=\"Another platfrom\">\n</a>\n</center>\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/relations.png\" alt=\"Relations\">\n\n<center>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/motlin\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/button/motlin.png\" alt=\"Motlin required\">\n</a>\n</center>\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/about.png\" alt=\"About\">\n\n<center><img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/groups/library_and_api.png\" alt=\"Library and API\"></center>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/versions/26-1.png\" width=\"5%\" alt=\"26.1\">\n<img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/versions/26-1-1.png\" width=\"5%\" alt=\"26.1.1\">\n<img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/versions/26-1-2.png\" width=\"5%\" alt=\"26.1.2\">\n<img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/versions/26-2.png\" width=\"5%\" alt=\"26.2\">\n</center>\n\n### IleafCore\n\nThere's nothing to see here! This mod contains the behind-the-scenes magic that keeps my other mods running. Unless another mod asks for it, you probably don't need it. 😄\n\n### What does this mod add?\n\n- Abstraction between two mod loaders\n- Some prefabs for blocks, items and so on...\n- Useful methods used in my mods\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/faq.png\" alt=\"FAQ\">\n\n| Question                             | Answer                                                                               |\n| ------------------------------------ |:------------------------------------------------------------------------------------:|\n| Can I use this mod in my modpack?    | Of course! We do not restrict anyone from using our projects :D                      |\n| Will you port mod to version X?      | We port our mods only to newer versions from version that is now mainly supported (_**26.1+**_)|\n| When the mod gets new update?        | Once I will finish with it, I cannot say the exact date when it will happen.         |\n| Where can I report bugs or suggest my idea? | In our discord server, you can find it in links section.                      |\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/our_projects.png\" alt=\"Our Projects\">\n\n<center>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/colorful-paradise\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/icons/colorful_paradise.png\" width=\"25%\" alt=\"Colorful Paradise\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/motlin\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/icons/motlin.png\" width=\"25%\" alt=\"Motlin\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ileafcore\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/icons/ileafcore.png\" width=\"25%\" alt=\"IleafCore\">\n</a>\n</center>\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/credits.png\" alt=\"Credits\">\n\n**Developed by the IleafMC Team which is a part of IleafDevelopment.** <a href=\"https://discord.gg/AHPcRheFX9\" style=\"float: right;\">Stay in touch</a>\n\n**All rights reserved by IleafDevelopment.**",
